    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This example has been meticulously maintained with a recent VANOS service and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement already completed\u2014critical for this chassis. The drivetrain is paired with a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power delivery and tactile feedback. Suspension geometry is dialed in with upgraded bushings and adjustable dampers for improved turn-in and lateral stability. While displaying honest cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast car, the mechanical integrity remains sharp, offering the high-revving, linear throttle response this platform is celebrated for.",
