      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-loved daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though a few minor stone chips reflect its honest road history. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free, with all power features, climate control, and the infotainment system working exactly as they should. Mechanically, it\u2019s solid; the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts without hesitation, and it has been serviced regularly with a full log of recent maintenance. It\u2019s a reliable, comfortable ride that balances performance with practicality\u2014perfect for someone who values a car that has been cared for properly.",
